title: Deific Weapon
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

You zealously bear your deity’s favored weapon. 

If it’s uncommon, you gain access to it. 

If it’s a simple weapon, increase the damage die by one step (d4 to d6, d6 to d8, d8 to d10, d10 to d12).